Marcel Vibert https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marcel_Vibert 0 Marcel Vibert (2 November 1883 – 11 June 1959) was a French film actor. Vibert worked primarily in the French film industry, but in the late 1920s he also appeared in several British silent films including Moulin Rouge and Champagne. On 14 October 1930, Vibert married actress Hélène Darly. Marcel_Vibert ( 2_November_1883 – 11_June_1959 ) was a_French_film_actor .
